codex
The current solver is likely skipping the only viable secondary market and is also vulnerable to a false callback from the funding leg before the actual redeem path. I’m patching both: better market discovery/caching, and a cleaner flash-funded redeem sequence that resets callback state only for the vulnerable transfer.
